reviewText: This is really a great tape---it has to be, because it's Fodor.  After reading the other review I now believe the stars were accidentally marked incorrectly. The tape covers so much wonderful stuff about France, and there's a Travel Guide Book with it too!

In this movie will learn about churches,castles,museums,you will learn how cheese is made,as well as wine,perfume,,you will also meet fashion designers,winemakers,cheese,makeup designers,A famous cook,and you will learn travel tips at the end of the movie with this and much much more!
